# Blog category pagination

## Query params
- `blog_tab` — active category slug or `all`
- `blog_paged` — page number (1-based)

## Files
- `partials/parts/blog/pagination.php` — circular nav (prev/next `cynRed`, current `cynBlack`)
- `templates/blog.php` — `WP_Query` per tab, cards loop + pagination inline in tab panels

## Tab JS
`blogCategoryTabs.js` updates `blog_tab` via `history.replaceState` and clears `blog_paged` on tab switch.

## Pagination links
Include `#blog-categories` anchor for scroll after page load.
